# Documentation Workflow

1. Check if `README.md` exists and is up-to-date with the current feature set.
2. Ensure every PHP file has a brief doc comment at the top explaining its purpose.
3. Add JSDoc-style comments to all public JS functions.
4. Update `.context/roadmap.md` if any new features were added or completed.
5. Log a summary of today's work in `.context/daily_log.md`.
6. Verify the database schema documentation matches the actual MySQL tables.
